- block case_study_lead_content
  %p.lead
    Bellabox is a monthly Australian subscription service which sends you a surprise beauty box of upcoming and cult products. They came to Minitheory to overhaul their website, which didn’t meet their growing needs.

  %p.lead 
    Minitheory worked with the Bellabox team and a development partner to craft a seamless experience across their subscription, e-commerce and editorial websites. With the new website, subscribers can easily buy, leave feedback and read more about their products.

